{
  "_comment": [
    "Manual patches applied on top of the generated command_schema.json.",
    "Use 'python scripts/generate_command_schema.py ... --patches scripts/schema_patches.json'",
    "to regenerate with these fixes preserved.",
    "",
    "Each entry under 'commands' REPLACES the corresponding key in the generated command.",
    "Only the listed keys are overwritten; all other generated data is preserved.",
    "",
    "Why these patches exist:",
    "  - Joint i/j marker groups: language.src incorrectly groups i_marker_name,",
    "    i_part_name, j_marker_name, j_part_name into a single 4-member exclusive group.",
    "    The correct Adams semantics are TWO independent groups: {i_marker_name, i_part_name}",
    "    (choose how to specify the I-body) and {j_marker_name, j_part_name} (J-body).",
    "    Using both i_marker_name AND j_marker_name is the normal, valid usage.",
    "  - Force/function groups: language.src omits the {function, user_function} exclusive",
    "    group entirely for force and data element commands. Both are marked required=True in",
    "    commands.exp, so without the group the linter fires E005 for the unused alternative.",
    "    Similarly, force create direct single_component_force needs i/j marker vs part groups."
  ],
  "commands": {
    "constraint create joint rigid": {
      "exclusive_groups": [
        {"group": 1, "members": ["i_marker_name", "i_part_name"]},
        {"group": 2, "members": ["j_marker_name", "j_part_name"]}
      ]
    },
    "constraint create joint translational": {
      "exclusive_groups": [
        {"group": 1, "members": ["i_marker_name", "i_part_name"]},
        {"group": 2, "members": ["j_marker_name", "j_part_name"]}
      ]
    },
    "constraint create joint revolute": {
      "exclusive_groups": [
        {"group": 1, "members": ["i_marker_name", "i_part_name"]},
        {"group": 2, "members": ["j_marker_name", "j_part_name"]}
      ]
    },
    "constraint create joint cylindrical": {
      "exclusive_groups": [
        {"group": 1, "members": ["i_marker_name", "i_part_name"]},
        {"group": 2, "members": ["j_marker_name", "j_part_name"]}
      ]
    },
    "constraint create joint universal": {
      "exclusive_groups": [
        {"group": 1, "members": ["i_marker_name", "i_part_name"]},
        {"group": 2, "members": ["j_marker_name", "j_part_name"]}
      ]
    },
    "constraint create joint spherical": {
      "exclusive_groups": [
        {"group": 1, "members": ["i_marker_name", "i_part_name"]},
        {"group": 2, "members": ["j_marker_name", "j_part_name"]}
      ]
